text: Potom my revealed ona this scripture truthfully confirming previous scriptures superseding them! Ona rule them v accordance s GOD's revelations nie nasledovat ich zelat they differ z truth pojdem ona! For each z ona my decreed zakon inak rites. Had GOD willed He robit ona 1 congregation. He thus puts ona test revelations He dat each z ona. Ona compete righteousness. Do GOD bol tvoj zaverecny destiny -all z ona -Potom He informovat ona z everything ona disputed
